Text: SENT ON BEHALF OF MIKE TELLEand Rosalie Attached hereto please find a final draft of the Term Sheet between the Houston Rockets and Sports Facilities LP At your earliest convenience please obtain the execution of four signature pages from this Term Sheet and either messenger the signature pages to me or call me and I will arrange for a messenger to pick the signatures pages up from you I will assemble executed sets of the Term Sheet for each party after I receive your signature pages If you have any questions or comments please contact me at Mike Telle v revised rockets term sheetDOC v revised rockets term sheetDOC v revised rockets term sheetDOC v revised rockets term sheetDOC
